Sex Videos Prompt Six More Turkey Candidates to Quit, CNN Says

-- B y   S e l c u k   G o k o l u k
-- 
2011-05-21T12:11:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-21/sex-videos-prompt-six-more-turkey-candidates-to-quit-cnn-says.html
Reports of sex videos allegedly
involving politicians from  Turkey ’s junior opposition party
Nationalist Action Party have led to the resignation of six
party candidates before the June 12 general elections, CNN Turk
reported.  Four party vice presidents as well as the general secretary
and the deputy general secretary resigned after sex videos were
released on the Internet, the television station said. All six
men were on the party’s electoral list, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Benjamin Harvey  in Ankara at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 